we still have to discuss the case,

10
00:01:43,590 --> 00:01:44,720
so we won't keep you.

11
00:01:45,479 --> 00:01:46,759
Well, one more thing.

12
00:01:46,900 --> 00:01:47,910
See if you can

13
00:01:48,140 --> 00:01:50,820
give this letter to him for me.

14
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:51,570
No, we can't.

15
00:01:52,190 --> 00:01:52,830
Hmm...

16
00:01:52,910 --> 00:01:54,870
The content of this letter is nothing special

17
00:01:54,870 --> 00:01:56,000
but just a few words,

18
00:01:56,020 --> 00:01:57,110
mainly telling him that

19
00:01:57,110 --> 00:01:59,110
the kid is doing well at home.

20
00:01:59,130 --> 00:02:00,330
Tell him not to worry.

21
00:02:00,370 --> 00:02:01,390
What's more,

22
00:02:01,420 --> 00:02:02,930
uh, in that court,

23
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:04,590
don't admit what he shouldn't admit.

24
00:02:04,590 --> 00:02:05,800
Okay. How about this?

25
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:08,190
Leave this letter here.

26
00:02:08,310 --> 00:02:08,870
Okay.

27
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:11,740
We need to discuss the case

28
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:13,080
and won't keep you.

29
00:02:15,020 --> 00:02:15,490
Okay.

30
00:02:15,510 --> 00:02:16,329
Okay, bye.

31
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,710
Everyone,

32
00:02:21,190 --> 00:02:22,520
I am counting on you

33
00:02:22,550 --> 00:02:23,680
to save Dafu's life!

34
00:02:23,870 --> 00:02:24,770
Please, thank you a lot.

35
00:02:24,770 --> 00:02:25,340
Okay.

36
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:26,270
Don't worry.

37
00:02:26,390 --> 00:02:27,320
I'll see you out.

38
00:02:29,290 --> 00:02:29,950
Luo Yingzi.

39
00:02:32,030 --> 00:02:33,630
Come back and close the door.

40
00:02:34,310 --> 00:02:34,910
Mr. Han.

41
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,680
If a witness is found,

42
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,790
it means that Wang Dafu didn't have time to commit the crime.

43
00:02:38,790 --> 00:02:40,250
Can we overturn the case then?

44
00:02:40,250 --> 00:02:41,110
Close the door.

45
00:02:49,870 --> 00:02:50,320
Here.

46
00:02:50,780 --> 00:02:51,250
Sit.

47
00:02:57,740 --> 00:02:59,630
When you sent her out yesterday,

48
00:02:59,650 --> 00:03:00,830
did you tell her

49
00:03:00,830 --> 00:03:02,120
to find a witness?

50
00:03:03,390 --> 00:03:03,870
Yes.

51
00:03:04,310 --> 00:03:06,360
Didn't she say yesterday Wang Dafu

52
00:03:06,390 --> 00:03:08,190
was with her at that time ?

53
00:03:08,500 --> 00:03:08,890
Then...

54
00:03:08,890 --> 00:03:10,170
Do you want to kill me?

55
00:03:10,310 --> 00:03:12,030
You've only studied law for a few days.

56
00:03:12,030 --> 00:03:13,830
Is there no one in the whole law firm as capable as you?

57
00:03:13,830 --> 00:03:14,630
Mr. Han, I...

58
00:03:14,650 --> 00:03:15,280
You what?

59
00:03:15,550 --> 00:03:16,620
Do you know what you're doing now

60
00:03:16,620 --> 00:03:17,940
will put us in jail?

61
00:03:18,350 --> 00:03:19,950
Mr. Han, I don't understand.

62
00:03:20,070 --> 00:03:21,329
You don't understand?

63
00:03:22,990 --> 00:03:25,320
Qiu Hua, explain it to her.

64
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:29,280
Witnesses and testimony

65
00:03:29,590 --> 00:03:31,550
are actually very unreliable.

66
00:03:32,570 --> 00:03:34,390
Sun Xiaoe  is determined to save her husband.

67
00:03:34,390 --> 00:03:36,360
and she also knows the importance of another witness.

68
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:39,270
she will definitely ask the villagers to help her make false testimony.

69
00:03:39,270 --> 00:03:41,340
If the villagers can't bring themselves to reject her,

70
00:03:41,340 --> 00:03:43,250
they will agree to testify for her.

71
00:03:43,250 --> 00:03:46,430
But this kind of testimony can't stand the court's cross-examination.

72
00:03:46,430 --> 00:03:48,579
When those witnesses meet the police,

73
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:51,570
and know that making false testimony is illegal,

74
00:03:51,950 --> 00:03:53,829
they may change their testimony.

75
00:03:54,730 --> 00:03:55,590
Think about it.

76
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,140
When they meet the police,

77
00:03:58,720 --> 00:04:01,450
and know that making false testimony is illegal,

78
00:04:01,630 --> 00:04:03,610
who will they blame for perjury?

79
00:04:05,810 --> 00:04:08,010
Do you know Article 306 of Criminal Law?

80
00:04:08,090 --> 00:04:08,660
Yes.

81
00:04:10,220 --> 00:04:11,570
In a criminal lawsuit,

82
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,790
defense lawyers and legal representatives

83
00:04:13,790 --> 00:04:15,520
who destroy or forge evidence,

84
00:04:16,050 --> 00:04:18,380
or help their clients destroy and forge evidence,

85
00:04:18,380 --> 00:04:20,839
threaten or induce witnesses against the truth

86
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:23,700
to change their testimony or make false testimony,

87
00:04:23,810 --> 00:04:26,830
shall be sentenced to fixed-term imprisonment of not more than three years or detention.

88
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:28,020
Severe violators

89
00:04:28,050 --> 00:04:32,170
shall be sentenced to fixed-term imprisonment of not less than three years but not more than seven years.

90
00:04:32,170 --> 00:04:33,900
You recite the terms very well.

91
00:04:34,700 --> 00:04:36,700
Mei Daliang is your teacher, right?

92
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,150
Do you know how Mei Daliang

93
00:04:38,150 --> 00:04:39,770
became like this?

94
00:04:42,010 --> 00:04:42,820
This law firm

95
00:04:43,180 --> 00:04:45,510
was founded by her, her husband

96
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:48,570
and Fang Lihong.

97
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:51,960
Afterwards, the couple took on a case,

98
00:04:52,780 --> 00:04:53,880
thinking they had obtained the testimony

99
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:56,710
that could overturn the nature of the case.

100
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:00,130
However, in court,

101
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:02,350
the witness insisted

102
00:05:02,370 --> 00:05:04,900
she instigated them to make false testimony.

103
00:05:04,940 --> 00:05:07,700
Her client also said in court

104
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:11,820
that she had incited them to change their guilty confession.

105
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,930
They were accused of

106
00:05:15,420 --> 00:05:18,530
violating Article 306 of Criminal Law.

107
00:05:22,700 --> 00:05:25,430
Yu Daliang collapsed on the spot in court

108
00:05:25,950 --> 00:05:28,280
due to a cerebral hemorrhage.

109
00:05:29,220 --> 00:05:32,020
Mei Daliang's lawyer's license was also revoked.

110
00:05:33,390 --> 00:05:35,780
Mei Daliang was originally named Mei Qin,

111
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:37,990
and she changed her name

112
00:05:38,050 --> 00:05:41,150
to commemorate her husband.

113
00:05:45,610 --> 00:05:46,850
You are still young.

114
00:05:48,260 --> 00:05:48,860
Remember,

115
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:51,280
As a lawyer,

116
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:54,080
your first opponent is your client.

117
00:05:55,460 --> 00:05:57,720
The second one is your opposite counsel.

118
00:05:57,750 --> 00:05:59,350
And the last one is the judge.

119
00:06:02,030 --> 00:06:02,660
Got it.

120
00:06:03,930 --> 00:06:04,790
Got it, Mr. Han.

121
00:06:10,470 --> 00:06:11,470
Qiu Hua, stay put.

122
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,580
Luo Yingzi, come with me.

123
00:06:13,580 --> 00:06:14,260
Mr. Han,

124
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,120
aren't you going to help with this?

125
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:18,600
If you let the bailiff check it out,

126
00:06:18,630 --> 00:06:19,600
and have a look...

127
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:21,860
I just looked at it and it's just a few words of family talk.

128
00:06:21,860 --> 00:06:23,010
Well,

129
00:06:23,270 --> 00:06:24,750
if you let Wang Dafu see it,

130
00:06:24,790 --> 00:06:25,770
it might calm him down.

131
00:06:25,770 --> 00:06:26,390
No way.

132
00:06:27,150 --> 00:06:28,030
I warned you

133
00:06:28,940 --> 00:06:30,670
not to make unnecessary moves.

134
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:33,020
Qiu Hua archives this letter.

135
00:06:41,950 --> 00:06:44,860
[Chengxi Detention Center]

136
00:06:46,850 --> 00:06:47,650
Face the wall.

137
00:06:51,420 --> 00:06:51,980
Let's go.

138
00:07:08,620 --> 00:07:11,800
[Meeting Room]

139
00:07:10,530 --> 00:07:11,200
Wang Dafu,

140
00:07:12,030 --> 00:07:13,230
We are the lawyers

141
00:07:13,230 --> 00:07:14,710
assigned to you by the Legal Aid Center.

142
00:07:14,710 --> 00:07:15,780
My name is Han Zhitong.

143
00:07:15,780 --> 00:07:17,040
Her name is Luo Yingzi.

144
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:20,410
do you agree to let us represent you?

145
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:23,440
Yes, yes, yes.

146
00:07:21,890 --> 00:07:25,900
[Defendant Wang Dafu]

147
00:07:24,860 --> 00:07:25,790
Counsels,

148
00:07:25,850 --> 00:07:27,710
I really didn't kill this person.

149
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:30,870
Get the power of attorney for him to sign.

150
00:07:30,870 --> 00:07:31,310
Okay.

151
00:07:39,430 --> 00:07:40,230
Here you are.

152
00:07:40,470 --> 00:07:42,130
Here's the power of attorney.

153
00:07:42,150 --> 00:07:43,210
Please take a look.

154
00:07:43,250 --> 00:07:44,120
If you agree...

155
00:07:44,150 --> 00:07:45,670
No, no need to read.

156
00:07:46,510 --> 00:07:47,640
I'll sign it.

157
00:07:48,140 --> 00:07:49,590
Then we can be

158
00:07:49,610 --> 00:07:50,830
your defense lawyers.

159
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:53,950
Our work will be done

160
00:07:54,030 --> 00:07:55,630
at the end of the first trial.

161
00:07:55,630 --> 00:07:56,640
No problem.

162
00:07:56,860 --> 00:07:57,590
Well, counsels,

163
00:07:57,590 --> 00:08:00,130
I really didn't kill this person.

164
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:02,740
This really has nothing to do with me.

165
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,110
Record it.

166
00:08:04,730 --> 00:08:05,770
I admit

167
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:09,290
my relationship with Qin Ailian

168
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:13,270
was a bit...improper.

169
00:08:13,820 --> 00:08:16,550
She kept forcing me to divorce,

170
00:08:16,580 --> 00:08:17,700
and I ignored her.

171
00:08:18,290 --> 00:08:19,550
Just the night before,

172
00:08:19,550 --> 00:08:21,640
because of the affair,

173
00:08:21,670 --> 00:08:22,710
my wife also quarreled with me,

174
00:08:22,710 --> 00:08:24,740
and then she went back to her mother's home.

175
00:08:24,740 --> 00:08:26,550
Then I was thinking

176
00:08:26,750 --> 00:08:28,990
whether to call my wife back or not.

177
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:29,830
And then,

178
00:08:29,830 --> 00:08:31,580
Qin Ailian came to me again.

179
00:08:31,900 --> 00:08:32,740
and then

180
00:08:32,780 --> 00:08:36,690
I couldn't resist the temptation,

181
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:39,590
and I slept with her again.

182
00:08:39,900 --> 00:08:42,400
After that, she got excited,

183
00:08:42,429 --> 00:08:44,740
and forced me to divorce once again.

184
00:08:44,780 --> 00:08:46,770
She made a fuss and started to fight.

185
00:08:46,770 --> 00:08:48,180
She scratched

186
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:50,050
my face and body several times.

187
00:08:50,430 --> 00:08:52,470
Later, I slapped her.

188
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,350
Then just at this time,

189
00:08:54,380 --> 00:08:55,850
the hotel where my wife works

190
00:08:55,850 --> 00:08:56,810
called me,

191
00:08:56,830 --> 00:08:58,660
and said that my wife hadn't been to work all day,

192
00:08:58,660 --> 00:09:00,670
and if she didn't go to work again, she would be fired.

193
00:09:00,670 --> 00:09:02,150
I was shocked.

194
00:09:02,180 --> 00:09:02,850
So I hurried out

195
00:09:02,850 --> 00:09:05,240
to find my wife.

196
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:09,470
I left at 1 p.m.

197
00:09:07,980 --> 00:09:11,730
[1 p.m., July 12]

198
00:09:09,830 --> 00:09:11,630
And when I came back, it was 7 p.m.

199
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:12,590
When I came back,

200
00:09:12,590 --> 00:09:14,710
she was already dead.

201
00:09:12,970 --> 00:09:17,540
[7 p.m., July 12]

202
00:09:31,570 --> 00:09:33,340
So I called the police.

203
00:09:33,700 --> 00:09:35,490
Then they insisted

204
00:09:35,710 --> 00:09:36,930
that I killed him.

205
00:09:37,020 --> 00:09:38,390
Well, counsels,

206
00:09:38,410 --> 00:09:40,130
you have to help me.

207
00:09:40,340 --> 00:09:41,630
If I wanted to kill her,

208
00:09:41,660 --> 00:09:42,350
why would I

209
00:09:42,370 --> 00:09:44,770
kill her in my own house?

210
00:09:45,110 --> 00:09:47,870
What's more, what happened between Qin Ailian and me

211
00:09:47,870 --> 00:09:49,590
was known to my wife.

212
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:51,110
So I didn't need to...

213
00:09:51,230 --> 00:09:51,860
You know?

214
00:09:52,270 --> 00:09:56,130
The legal term for that is motive.

215
00:09:52,550 --> 00:09:55,880
[Wang Dafu 500,000 yuan]

216
00:09:56,160 --> 00:09:57,290
I have no motive.

217
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,220
I haven't...

218
00:09:58,250 --> 00:09:59,240
I haven't had a motive.

219
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,170
No motive.

220
00:10:00,620 --> 00:10:01,020
Okay.

221
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:02,290
We got it.

222
00:10:03,690 --> 00:10:04,720
When the police asked you,

223
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,840
did you tell this to them?

224
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:06,790
Yes.

225
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:09,990
Wang Dafu.

226
00:10:11,830 --> 00:10:15,190
Now the prosecution believes that you killed the person,

227
00:10:15,490 --> 00:10:17,620
and the evidence is quite sufficient.

228
00:10:18,420 --> 00:10:19,760
we will bring up what you said

229
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:21,630
when we defend you.

230
00:10:22,250 --> 00:10:23,490
But in my opinion,

231
00:10:23,870 --> 00:10:25,450
it's almost impossible

232
00:10:25,830 --> 00:10:27,560
to put on a non-guilty defense.

233
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:29,420
Well, why is it impossible?

234
00:10:29,710 --> 00:10:30,610
Counsels...

235
00:10:31,350 --> 00:10:33,710
If you plead guilty with a good attitude,

236
00:10:33,790 --> 00:10:34,950
repent sincerely,

237
00:10:35,130 --> 00:10:37,650
actively compensate the victim,

238
00:10:37,810 --> 00:10:40,410
and get forgiveness from the victim's family,

239
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:43,760
it'll be helpful for your sentence reduction in the end.

240
00:10:43,990 --> 00:10:45,350
Well, counsels,

241
00:10:45,370 --> 00:10:48,240
I really didn't kill her.

242
00:10:49,670 --> 00:10:52,350
The civil litigator proposed that

243
00:10:52,730 --> 00:10:54,700
if your family could offer 500,000 yuan,

244
00:10:54,700 --> 00:10:58,230
the victim's family will issue a letter of understanding,

245
00:10:58,820 --> 00:11:01,480
which will be very helpful for your sentencing.

246
00:11:03,330 --> 00:11:05,240
Where could I get the money?

247
00:11:05,890 --> 00:11:06,420
No.

248
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:07,630
Well, uh...

249
00:11:07,660 --> 00:11:09,540
Let's sort it out.

250
00:11:09,830 --> 00:11:11,010
I didn't kill her.

251
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:12,640
Why should I compensate her?

252
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:14,240
Do you have any evidence

253
00:11:14,260 --> 00:11:15,990
to prove what you said?

254
00:11:17,300 --> 00:11:17,850
No.

255
00:11:19,230 --> 00:11:20,380
I can't remember.

256
00:11:20,910 --> 00:11:21,750
You just said

257
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:24,240
you went out at 1 p.m.

258
00:11:25,180 --> 00:11:27,530
But there's no surveillance footage of it.

259
00:11:27,530 --> 00:11:28,930
How can you explain that?

260
00:11:29,190 --> 00:11:30,600
How did you leave?

261
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:32,520
The place where we live,

262
00:11:32,540 --> 00:11:34,800
the urban villages on the edge of the city

263
00:11:35,090 --> 00:11:37,210
are mostly illegal buildings.

264
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,520
They may be demolished at any time.

265
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:40,460
How could there be surveillance footage?

266
00:11:40,460 --> 00:11:41,320
Wang Dafu.

267
00:11:41,380 --> 00:11:43,240
Lawsuits are all about evidence.

268
00:11:43,290 --> 00:11:44,990
If you say you didn't kill anyone,

269
00:11:44,990 --> 00:11:45,830
you have to

270
00:11:45,870 --> 00:11:48,270
find evidence that you didn't kill anyone.

271
00:11:48,390 --> 00:11:49,770
You can think about it again.

272
00:11:49,770 --> 00:11:51,160
If you think of anything,

273
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:52,400
tell us in time.

274
00:11:52,870 --> 00:11:54,660
-Yes. Yes.
-Seize your time.

275
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:55,600
Well,

276
00:11:56,470 --> 00:11:58,720
Well, counsels, please don't go.

277
00:11:58,900 --> 00:11:59,850
I'm innocent.

278
00:11:59,870 --> 00:12:01,880
No, don't go, counsels.

279
00:12:16,730 --> 00:12:18,260
Luo Yingzi, what do you mean?

280
00:12:18,260 --> 00:12:20,040
What I said to you on the way was all in vain.

281
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:21,550
Mr. Han, let me explain.

282
00:12:21,590 --> 00:12:22,550
Explain what?

283
00:12:22,790 --> 00:12:25,450
Do you know what you're doing is very dangerous?

284
00:12:25,710 --> 00:12:28,190
He's in prison now.

285
00:12:28,410 --> 00:12:30,520
What's in it for him if he lies?

286
