00:24:22,350 --> 00:24:23,610
You go with Luo Yingzi.

571
00:24:24,510 --> 00:24:25,110
Remember.

572
00:24:25,430 --> 00:24:26,510
You can only listen to him.

573
00:24:26,510 --> 00:24:27,640
Don't say anything.

574
00:24:29,360 --> 00:24:29,920
Okay.

575
00:24:36,830 --> 00:24:38,870
Sorry for troubling you.

576
00:24:39,060 --> 00:24:39,660
It's okay.

577
00:24:40,040 --> 00:24:41,970
But it's useless for us to go there.

578
00:24:42,920 --> 00:24:43,670
Why?

579
00:24:44,420 --> 00:24:45,140
Pupils

580
00:24:45,160 --> 00:24:46,960
can't meet clients alone.

581
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:49,220
The detention center won't let us in.

582
00:24:49,950 --> 00:24:52,670
Then, why did Mr. Han ask us to go?

583
00:24:53,560 --> 00:24:54,750
He's afraid of trouble.

584
00:24:54,750 --> 00:24:56,890
We'll meet the client only once before trial.

585
00:24:56,890 --> 00:24:59,290
It'll be a failure and we'll soon come back.

586
00:25:00,910 --> 00:25:01,600
Wait.

587
00:25:01,910 --> 00:25:03,680
Wait, Ms. Qiu.

588
00:25:10,480 --> 00:25:11,320
Mr. Han,

589
00:25:11,830 --> 00:25:14,830
I'm afraid you have to come here in person.

590
00:25:15,020 --> 00:25:17,200
Pupils can't meet clients alone.

591
00:25:17,300 --> 00:25:18,670
Just come back if you can't meet him.

592
00:25:18,670 --> 00:25:19,570
We've already been there.

593
00:25:19,570 --> 00:25:20,850
You'd better come.

594
00:25:20,880 --> 00:25:23,540
Maybe we'll see him only this time before trial.

595
00:25:23,730 --> 00:25:24,820
I'm busy right now.

596
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:27,840
So should I tell them

597
00:25:27,980 --> 00:25:30,900
the suspect wants to meet the lawyer,

598
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:32,190
but the lawyer refuses to come?

599
00:25:32,190 --> 00:25:33,950
The lawyers know that pupils can't meet clients alone.

600
00:25:33,950 --> 00:25:35,620
I'll call you back.

601
00:25:36,020 --> 00:25:39,900
But he still sends a pupil there.

602
00:25:43,990 --> 00:25:44,760
Luo Yingzi.

603
00:25:45,370 --> 00:25:46,610
You've grown up.

604
00:25:48,440 --> 00:25:49,280
I'll drive.

605
00:25:49,480 --> 00:25:50,810
We'll be back soon.

606
00:25:53,650 --> 00:25:54,320
Ms. Qiu.

607
00:25:59,000 --> 00:26:01,190
Mr. Han, so I don't need to go.

608
00:26:01,210 --> 00:26:02,270
Let's go together.

609
00:26:04,350 --> 00:26:05,350
Let's go, Ms. Qiu.

610
00:26:13,520 --> 00:26:14,480
You wait here.

611
00:26:19,610 --> 00:26:21,990
[Meeting Room]

612
00:26:20,850 --> 00:26:22,050
I remember one thing.

613
00:26:22,680 --> 00:26:24,850
When I went out,

614
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:27,480
I ran into my next-door neighbor, Niu.

615
00:26:28,150 --> 00:26:29,240
He and I are quite close.

616
00:26:29,240 --> 00:26:30,720
He was an illegal taxi driver.

617
00:26:30,720 --> 00:26:32,050
When his child was sick,

618
00:26:32,070 --> 00:26:33,300
I gave him 100 yuan.

619
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:35,160
So when Niu saw me, he said

620
00:26:35,190 --> 00:26:36,450
he could give me a ride.

621
00:26:40,410 --> 00:26:41,030
Okay.

622
00:26:42,250 --> 00:26:42,850
Wang.

623
00:26:43,070 --> 00:26:44,600
What happened to your face?

624
00:26:45,190 --> 00:26:46,000
A long story.

625
00:26:46,420 --> 00:26:47,500
Let's go. Go.

626
00:26:47,940 --> 00:26:48,650
Okay.

627
00:26:49,580 --> 00:26:51,180
Wang, fasten your seat belt.

628
00:26:56,350 --> 00:26:57,870
Later I thought

629
00:26:58,100 --> 00:27:01,130
my presence in the car would affect his business.

630
00:27:01,470 --> 00:27:03,650
So I lied.

631
00:27:03,670 --> 00:27:04,550
I said I had arrived

632
00:27:04,550 --> 00:27:05,780
and I got off early.

633
00:27:06,240 --> 00:27:06,990
After getting off,

634
00:27:06,990 --> 00:27:08,850
I was on the way to my wife's house.

635
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:14,640
There was a dump truck on the road.

636
00:27:14,730 --> 00:27:16,750
Someone was fixing the truck underneath it.

637
00:27:16,750 --> 00:27:17,710
When I passed by,

638
00:27:17,710 --> 00:27:19,310
he asked me to get him a spanner.

639
00:27:19,310 --> 00:27:21,070
So I gave him a favor.

640
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:22,440
Is this it?

641
00:27:22,460 --> 00:27:22,920
Yes.

642
00:27:23,990 --> 00:27:24,990
Okay, thank you.

643
00:27:28,690 --> 00:27:29,980
At that time,

644
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:30,790
I didn't know

645
00:27:30,790 --> 00:27:32,800
how to explain the injury on my face to my wife.

646
00:27:32,800 --> 00:27:34,230
I was pondering on one side

647
00:27:34,230 --> 00:27:35,720
and on the other,

648
00:27:35,750 --> 00:27:36,830
I just chatted with him casually.

649
00:27:36,830 --> 00:27:39,070
It should be around 2 p.m at that time.

650
00:27:39,890 --> 00:27:40,390
That...

651
00:27:40,420 --> 00:27:41,570
The car mechanic.

652
00:27:41,590 --> 00:27:44,220
He can help me prove where I was then.

653
00:27:44,360 --> 00:27:45,290
What's his name?

654
00:27:45,600 --> 00:27:46,530
Where is he from?

655
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:48,170
I don't know.

656
00:27:48,200 --> 00:27:50,210
He's just a stranger I bumped into.

657
00:27:50,230 --> 00:27:51,150
I didn't ask.

658
00:27:51,500 --> 00:27:53,560
What about the license plate number?

659
00:27:55,550 --> 00:27:57,600
I really didn't notice it.

660
00:27:57,950 --> 00:27:59,960
After he came out,

661
00:27:59,990 --> 00:28:01,560
we exchanged cigarettes

662
00:28:01,590 --> 00:28:02,430
and had a chat.

663
00:28:02,460 --> 00:28:03,460
Then I left.

664
00:28:03,990 --> 00:28:05,910
I really didn't notice the plate number.

665
00:28:05,910 --> 00:28:06,390
Well...

666
00:28:06,630 --> 00:28:08,260
Niu can testify for you.

667
00:28:09,560 --> 00:28:11,400
That's why I'm unlucky.

668
00:28:11,600 --> 00:28:13,590
When I went home,

669
00:28:13,610 --> 00:28:16,090
I saw a bunch of people surrounding Niu's house.

670
00:28:16,090 --> 00:28:17,330
So I went up and asked.

671
00:28:17,620 --> 00:28:20,140
That's when I found out that Niu,

672
00:28:20,350 --> 00:28:21,220
who drove an illegal car,

673
00:28:21,220 --> 00:28:23,510
happened to run into people checking illegal taxis that afternoon.

674
00:28:23,510 --> 00:28:24,710
He drove away.

675
00:28:24,940 --> 00:28:26,450
In a moment of inattention,

676
00:28:26,450 --> 00:28:27,460
he and his car

677
00:28:27,480 --> 00:28:28,800
flipped off the bridge

678
00:28:28,800 --> 00:28:30,710
and into the ditch.

679
00:28:30,710 --> 00:28:31,190
So...

680
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:33,320
He was drowned.

681
00:28:35,390 --> 00:28:36,060
Wang Dafu.

682
00:28:36,090 --> 00:28:36,950
Anything else?

683
00:28:37,510 --> 00:28:38,350
Well...

684
00:28:38,640 --> 00:28:40,720
When I left my wife's house,

685
00:28:40,750 --> 00:28:43,520
it was around 4:00 p.m.

686
00:28:43,810 --> 00:28:44,930
I heard

687
00:28:44,960 --> 00:28:47,230
someone playing the woodwinds on the side of the road down the mountain.

688
00:28:47,230 --> 00:28:49,150
It was an old song

689
00:28:49,910 --> 00:28:51,710
called "Lift the Bridal Sedan".

690
00:28:54,520 --> 00:28:56,400
Did you see who was playing it?

691
00:28:57,170 --> 00:28:57,690
No.

692
00:28:57,720 --> 00:28:58,920
It was quite far away.

693
00:29:00,800 --> 00:29:01,740
Is there anything else?

694
00:29:01,740 --> 00:29:03,270
And my wife.

695
00:29:03,670 --> 00:29:04,920
My wife...

696
00:29:04,960 --> 00:29:07,180
She should be able to hear

697
00:29:07,240 --> 00:29:08,200
the that sound as well.

698
00:29:08,200 --> 00:29:09,890
You can ask my wife.

699
00:29:10,470 --> 00:29:11,010
Wang Dafu.

700
00:29:11,010 --> 00:29:11,800
Wang Dafu.

701
00:29:12,300 --> 00:29:13,450
The victim proposed

702
00:29:13,670 --> 00:29:14,870
if your family

703
00:29:14,900 --> 00:29:17,820
would offer 500,000 yuan,

704
00:29:18,230 --> 00:29:21,670
the victim's family can submit a letter of understanding.

705
00:29:22,530 --> 00:29:23,870
With this letter,

706
00:29:24,290 --> 00:29:27,690
there's a higher chance that you won't be sentenced to death.

707
00:29:27,870 --> 00:29:28,860
Can your family pay the money?

708
00:29:28,860 --> 00:29:30,320
Well, Mr. Han...

709
00:29:30,980 --> 00:29:32,650
I didn't kill her.

710
00:29:32,690 --> 00:29:34,290
Why should I compensate her?

711
00:29:35,280 --> 00:29:35,610
Okay.

712
00:29:36,010 --> 00:29:37,540
I see.

713
00:29:38,110 --> 00:29:38,600
No.

714
00:29:39,840 --> 00:29:40,630
This thing.

715
00:29:41,310 --> 00:29:43,070
We've already informed you of that.

716
00:29:43,070 --> 00:29:43,960
Yes. Yes. Yes.

717
00:29:45,560 --> 00:29:46,230
No.

718
00:29:46,480 --> 00:29:47,000
No.

719
00:29:47,020 --> 00:29:47,550
Let's go.

720
00:29:47,870 --> 00:29:48,330
This...

721
00:29:49,580 --> 00:29:51,440
Wait, why? Why do you leave again?

722
00:29:51,990 --> 00:29:52,990
Wait, Mr. Han.

723
00:29:53,240 --> 00:29:55,570
Mr. Han. I really didn't kill this person.

724
00:29:56,010 --> 00:29:57,900
Wait, Ms. Luo, you can look into this matter,

725
00:29:57,900 --> 00:29:59,090
and it will become clear.

726
00:29:59,090 --> 00:30:00,670
I really didn't kill this person.

727
00:30:00,670 --> 00:30:01,790
I'm innocent.

728
00:30:06,660 --> 00:30:09,080
I need to meet a client.

729
00:30:09,150 --> 00:30:10,700
You two go back by yourselves.

730
00:30:10,700 --> 00:30:11,160
Mr. Han,

731
00:30:11,450 --> 00:30:13,560
I still want to talk to you.

732
00:30:13,750 --> 00:30:15,100
Do you think we can

733
00:30:15,130 --> 00:30:16,820
ask Wang Dafu's wife

734
00:30:17,030 --> 00:30:19,070
if she heard the music?

735
00:30:19,230 --> 00:30:21,380
Why wouldn't you just listen to me?

736
00:30:21,790 --> 00:30:22,280
I...

737
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:24,000
Qiu Hua, tell her.

738
00:30:24,670 --> 00:30:25,250
Don't ask her.

739
00:30:25,250 --> 00:30:27,310
If you do, she'll definitely say yes.

740
00:30:27,850 --> 00:30:28,770
What should we do?

741
00:30:28,770 --> 00:30:30,130
We have no choice.

742
00:30:30,340 --> 00:30:32,260
There's nothing to defend about this case.

743
00:30:32,260 --> 00:30:33,440
Of course, you can raise your doubts.

744
00:30:33,440 --> 00:30:34,900
The court won't accept it.

745
00:30:35,150 --> 00:30:36,280
I'll say this again:

746
00:30:36,510 --> 00:30:37,070
in this case,

747
00:30:37,070 --> 00:30:38,710
he will be lucky enough

748
00:30:38,710 --> 00:30:41,040
not to be executed immediately, you know?

749
00:30:41,450 --> 00:30:42,650
Okay, you can go back.

750
00:30:50,360 --> 00:30:51,040
Ms. Qiu.

751
00:30:52,420 --> 00:30:54,950
Listen to him. Is this what a lawyer should do?

752
00:30:55,140 --> 00:30:57,470
Mr. Han has always been a lawyer like this.

753
00:30:57,710 --> 00:30:58,510
But shouldn't we

754
00:30:58,510 --> 00:31:00,910
be responsible for the interest of the client?

755
00:31:00,910 --> 00:31:02,720
He's responsible enough

756
00:31:02,750 --> 00:31:04,120
to come with you today.

757
00:31:04,660 --> 00:31:05,260
Let's go.

758
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:27,540
He's struggling in desperation,

759
00:31:27,910 --> 00:31:30,060
trying to use his lawyers to buy him time

760
00:31:30,060 --> 00:31:31,680
as long as possible.

761
00:31:33,630 --> 00:31:34,470
What he said

762
00:31:34,650 --> 00:31:37,580
shouldn't be mentioned in the statement of defense.

763
00:31:39,450 --> 00:31:40,710
The trial is coming up.

764
00:31:41,490 --> 00:31:42,240
Next Monday,

765
00:31:43,200 --> 00:31:45,360
you'll write up that defense and give it to me.

766
00:31:45,360 --> 00:31:46,600
Six days left. Go.

767
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:48,280
Mr. Han,

768
00:31:48,380 --> 00:31:49,500
it's not that I'm stubborn.

769
00:31:49,500 --> 00:31:50,800
I just feel that

770
00:31:50,830 --> 00:31:52,950
Wang Dafu doesn't seem to be lying to us.

771
00:31:52,950 --> 00:31:54,650
What kind of lies can't he tell?

772
00:31:54,650 --> 00:31:56,690
He insisted on saying these unreliable things.

773
00:31:56,690 --> 00:31:57,740
Doesn't he know

774
00:31:57,760 --> 00:31:59,950
it's useless if we can't prove it?

775
00:32:00,160 --> 00:32:01,150
When people are desperate,

776
00:32:01,150 --> 00:32:02,900
they can come up with any idea.

777
00:32:03,380 --> 00:32:04,680
If he says something reliable,

778
00:32:04,680 --> 00:32:06,810
we find it doesn't happen.

779
00:32:07,720 --> 00:32:09,630
He knew we couldn't find it out.

780
00:32:10,030 --> 00:32:12,550
If we believe him, we will ask for an extension

781
00:32:12,550 --> 00:32:13,390
and keep investigating.

782
00:32:13,390 --> 00:32:15,120
Then his goal will be achieved.

783
00:32:15,390 --> 00:32:17,390
There are plenty of ways for a client

784
00:32:17,430 --> 00:32:18,790
to fool the lawyer.

785
00:32:18,900 --> 00:32:19,900
Learn the lesson.

786
00:32:25,530 --> 00:32:26,100
Mr. Han.

787
00:32:26,760 --> 00:32:27,480
Well,

788
00:32:27,570 --> 00:32:29,590
you just mentioned there's still a week left.

789
00:32:29,590 --> 00:32:30,920
Why don't you let me

790
00:32:30,940 --> 00:32:32,320
use this week to investigate?

791
00:32:32,320 --> 00:32:33,720
You're so stubborn.

792
00:32:34,710 --> 00:32:36,160
I just feel uneasy.

793
00:32:36,190 --> 00:32:38,540
I don't think he's lying to us.

794
00:32:40,910 --> 00:32:41,640
Fine.

795
00:32:41,670 --> 00:32:42,930
Go ahead if you want to.

796
00:32:43,030 --> 00:32:43,780
No.

797
00:32:44,320 --> 00:32:45,310
Not a week.

798
00:32:45,370 --> 00:32:46,240
Only six days.

799
00:32:46,560 --> 00:32:47,090
No.

800
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:48,960
You have to leave me one more day

801
00:32:48,990 --> 00:32:50,540
to revise the defense you wrote.

802
00:32:50,540 --> 00:32:51,980
So you only have five days.

803
00:32:51,980 --> 00:32:52,710
Understand?

804
00:32:55,580 --> 00:32:56,640
Thank you, Mr. Han.

805
00:32:57,670 --> 00:32:59,330
Are you still investigating?

806
00:32:59,400 --> 00:33:00,240
Yes.

807
00:33:06,330 --> 00:33:09,340
A woodwind player.

808
00:33:11,900 --> 00:33:14,290
A dump truck.

809
00:33:16,100 --> 00:33:18,330
Where can I find it?

810
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:27,590
Hello.

811
00:33:28,730 --> 00:33:29,450
Hello.

812
00:34:12,900 --> 00:34:15,449
I can't afford to take on cases on my own right now.

813
00:34:15,449 --> 00:34:17,280
Ms. Qiu, I need to...

814
00:34:18,300 --> 00:34:19,330
I need to talk to you.

815
00:34:19,330 --> 00:34:20,389
Can you come out?

816
00:34:21,639 --> 00:34:22,679
Mom, I am busy now.

817
00:34:22,710 --> 00:34:23,840
I'll call you later.

818
00:34:28,820 --> 00:34:29,620
What's wrong?

819
00:34:29,830 --> 00:34:30,580
What happened?

820
00:34:30,580 --> 00:34:31,239
Ms. Qiu.

821
00:34:32,469 --> 00:34:33,929
Something happened to me.

822
00:34:34,350 --> 00:34:35,150
What's wrong?

823
00:34:36,929 --> 00:34:39,050
I don't know who I can ask for help.

824
00:34:39,710 --> 00:34:40,739
I thought of you.

825
00:34:41,550 --> 00:34:42,670
Can you help me?

826
00:34:44,320 --> 00:34:45,000
Go ahead.

827
00:34:45,810 --> 00:34:47,090
To put it simply,

828
00:34:47,590 --> 00:34:49,800
my husband and a woman I know

829
00:34:50,610 --> 00:34:51,929
sneaked off together.

830
00:34:52,050 --> 00:34:53,820
They went to America together.

831
00:34:54,199 --> 00:34:56,320
Didn't you tell us you're divorced?

832
00:34:56,340 --> 00:34:56,860
Yes.

833
00:34:57,260 --> 00:34:59,690
I did file for a divorce.

834
00:35:00,180 --> 00:35:01,740
But I just found out

835
00:35:03,540 --> 00:35:05,270
he borrowed money from others.

836
00:35:07,110 --> 00:35:09,210
The creditor has called me for repayment.

837
00:35:09,210 --> 00:35:10,340
Who is the creditor?

838
00:35:10,720 --> 00:35:14,480
It's a quick loan. A personal loan.

839
00:35:15,030 --> 00:35:15,660
They told me

840
00:35:15,660 --> 00:35:18,190
he's borrowed hundreds of thousands yuan before

841
00:35:18,190 --> 00:35:19,820
and he's been paying back the interest.

842
00:35:19,820 --> 00:35:20,900
Then he ran away

843
00:35:21,330 --> 00:35:22,770
and never paid it back.

844
00:35:22,850 --> 00:35:25,580
So it's already gone to 800,000 yuan in a few days.

845
00:35:27,300 --> 00:35:28,910
The High Court of Justice has an interpretation of Article 24 of the Marriage Act.

846
00:35:28,910 --> 00:35:30,180
Did you know that?

847
00:35:30,480 --> 00:35:31,370
The creditors

848
00:35:31,770 --> 00:35:33,500
claiming rights to debts

849
00:35:34,030 --> 00:35:35,630
incurred by one of the spouses in his or her personal name

850
00:35:35,630 --> 00:35:37,870
during the marriage

851
00:35:37,900 --> 00:35:40,230
are treated as joint debts of the spouses.

852
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:43,270
However, it doesn't work if one of the spouses can prove that the creditor

853
00:35:43,270 --> 00:35:45,760
and the debtor have explicitly agreed that it is a personal debt

854
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:47,470
or can prove that it is one of the cases

